sd=Business Unit Management	Track and report on business unit activity and financial performance	A business unit consolidates activity and performance details for periodic internal management reporting	Handles the oversight and management of a general organizational business unit. This includes the definition and implementation of the management plan, overseeing ongoing activity and performance assessments and troubleshooting issues that might arise
sdpath=business-unit-management
crpath=business-unit-management-plan
crr=Business Unit Management Plan Instance
mcr=Business Unit Management Plan
bqs=Performance Troubleshooting
CONFIG
BusinessUnitManagementPlan	create	Create the management plan for the business unit		createBusinessUnitManagementPlan		#desc
BusinessUnitManagementPlan	update	Update aspects of the business unit management plan		updateBusinessUnitManagementPlan		#desc
BusinessUnitManagementPlan	exchange	Accept, reject, etc. aspects of the business unit management plan		exchangeBusinessUnitManagementPlan		#desc
BusinessUnitManagementPlan	request	Request manual intervention with the plan (e.g. reprioritize activities)		requestBusinessUnitManagementPlan		#desc
BusinessUnitManagementPlan	retrieve	Retrieve details about the business unit management plan		retrieveBusinessUnitManagementPlan		#desc
Performance	update	Update details of the activity analysis for the business unit	updateBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance	updateBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance		Update to any amendable fields of the Performance instance
Performance	request	Request manual intervention in the business unit performance analysis (e.g. revise projections)	requestBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance	requestBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance		Invoke a service request action against the Performance instance
Performance	retrieve	Retrieve details about the business unit activity analysis	retrieveBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance	retrieveBusinessUnitManagementPlanPerformance		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Performance instance related report
Troubleshooting	create	Create a service troubleshooting activity (to address major production issue)	createBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting	createBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting		Details of a new Troubleshooting instance
Troubleshooting	update	Update details of a troubleshooting plan item	updateBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting	updateBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting		Update to any amendable fields of the Troubleshooting instance
Troubleshooting	request	Request manual intervention to a troubleshooting action	requestBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting	requestBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting		Invoke a service request action against the Troubleshooting instance
Troubleshooting	retrieve	Retrieve details about troubleshooting activity	retrieveBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting	retrieveBusinessUnitManagementPlanTroubleshooting		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Troubleshooting instance related report
